search.views module¶

search.views.search(request)[source]¶

This method is used to get the specialty, doctor’s name and email from the search html form.

By matching the specialty and name, it retrieves doctor’s information from database to display in the results.

If search criteria is not matched from the database, it shows search is not found and gives option to search again.

Parameters

request (HttpResponse.) – It’s a HttpResponse from user.

Returns

This method returns a html page that displays the search results or shows search is not found.

Return type

HttpResponse.
